Uses of Package
spaska.analysis

  • Packages that use spaska.analysis 
    Package Description
    spaska.analysis
    A package that groups all analyzers operating on classifiers and clusterers.
    spaska.framework
    A package containing classes that help us implement the framework spaska as a whole.
    spaska.gui.engines
    A package containing different workflow/engines for our framework.
    spaska.statistics
    A package that contains statistics that are taken throughout the framework.
  • Classes in spaska.analysis used by spaska.analysis 
    Class and Description
    IAnalyzer
    An interface that represents all analyzers that can test the performance of a given classifier or other characteristics.
    ICompareAnalyzer
    An interface that represents all analyzers that operate on two classifiers and compare their performance.
    IStatisticalTest
    An interface representing statistical test analyzers that compare two classifiers.
    TestType
    Describes the types of tests applied to a hypothesis of the kind : H0: m == a H1: m a.
